<h3 class="index-h3">Plugin support</h3>

<p><strong>Woodpecker provide a communication channel between mac client and app, and defines the way they talk to each other, according the rule, we can custom a plugin very easily.</strong>
<a href="/plugin.html">Learn more.</a>
<br /></p>

